    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/models/gemini-3.1-flash-lite:generateContent",
        "authentication": "predefinedCredentialType",
        "nodeCredentialType": "googlePalmApi",
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"system_instruction\": {\n    \"parts\": [\n      {\n        \"text\": \"You are a UK supermarket receipt parser. You will be given a photo of a supermarket receipt. Extract all data and return ONLY valid JSON — no markdown, no explanation, no code fences.\\n\\nIDENTIFY THE STORE from the header (Aldi, Tesco, Sainsbury's, Asda, Morrisons, Lidl, Waitrose, M&S, Co-op, Costco, etc.).\\n\\nStore-specific rules:\\n- Aldi/Lidl: ignore 6-digit PLU codes before item names. A discount line immediately follows the item it applies to — treat it as is_discount_line=true and link discount_amount to the previous item.\\n- Tesco: use Clubcard price when shown, not the normal price.\\n- Sainsbury's: ignore Nectar points lines.\\n- Costco: items have a SKU number on the left (e.g. 2631, 464916). VAT code is the letter printed after the price — A=20% VAT (is_taxable=true, tax_rate_percent=20), Z=0% VAT (is_taxable=false, tax_rate_percent=0). Always use the VAT code from the receipt, do not infer VAT from the product category. If a price has a trailing minus (e.g. '1.00-Z'), output unit_price as -1.00 (negative) and set is_discount_line=true.\\n- All stores: prices are in the right column; item names in the left column.\\n\\nGeneral rules:\\n- Output pure numbers for all prices (2.49 not £2.49).\\n- quantity defaults to 1 if not shown.\\n- If a value is not clearly visible, use null — never guess.\\n- Discount lines: is_discount_line=true, discount_amount=positive number (amount saved).\\n- Date format: YYYY-MM-DD. Time format: HH:MM (24h).\\n- VAT: fresh produce/most food = 0%, hot food/snacks/alcohol = 20%.\\n- Ignore: loyalty ads, barcodes, survey codes, card **** numbers, thank-you lines, cashier names.\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"contents\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"parts\": [\n        {\n          \"inline_data\": {\n            \"mime_type\": \"{{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.attachments[0].content_type }}\",\n            \"data\": \"{{ $json.data }}\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"Parse this supermarket receipt and return JSON in this exact structure:\\n{\\n  \\\"store_name\\\": string,\\n  \\\"store_branch\\\": string | null,\\n  \\\"store_address\\\": string | null,\\n  \\\"store_postcode\\\": string | null,\\n  \\\"receipt_date\\\": string | null,\\n  \\\"receipt_time\\\": string | null,\\n  \\\"currency\\\": \\\"GBP\\\",\\n  \\\"subtotal\\\": number | null,\\n  \\\"discount_total\\\": number | null,\\n  \\\"tax_amount\\\": number | null,\\n  \\\"total_amount\\\": number | null,\\n  \\\"payment_method\\\": string | null,\\n  \\\"last4_card_digits\\\": string | null,\\n  \\\"loyalty_programme\\\": string | null,\\n  \\\"items\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"line_number\\\": number,\\n      \\\"product_name\\\": string,\\n      \\\"normalised_name\\\": string,\\n      \\\"category\\\": string,\\n      \\\"quantity\\\": number,\\n      \\\"unit\\\": string | null,\\n      \\\"unit_price\\\": number | null,\\n      \\\"line_total\\\": number | null,\\n      \\\"is_discount_line\\\": boolean,\\n      \\\"discount_amount\\\": number | null,\\n      \\\"is_taxable\\\": boolean,\\n      \\\"tax_rate_percent\\\": number,\\n      \\\"brand\\\": string | null,\\n      \\\"sku_or_barcode\\\": string | null\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"generationConfig\": {\n    \"temperature\": 0.1,\n    \"responseMimeType\": \"application/json\",\n    \"maxOutputTokens\": 8192\n  }\n}",
        "options": {
          "response": {
            "response": {
              "responseFormat": "json"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.3,
      "position": [
        -1968,
        112
      ],
      "id": "871c04ab-5117-48d2-b315-24c3f32c92b2",
      "name": "Gemini Vision LLM",
      "credentials": {
        "googlePalmApi": {
          "id": "rj11C9kBvF5GQPHA",
          "name": "Google Api Studio - Receipt-Mgt"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const raw = $json.candidates[0].content.parts[0].text;\n\n// Strip markdown fences if model adds them despite instructions\nconst cleaned = raw\n  .replace(/^```json\\s*/i, '')\n  .replace(/^```\\s*/i, '')\n  .replace(/```\\s*$/i, '')\n  .trim();\n\nlet parsed;\ntry {\n  parsed = JSON.parse(cleaned);\n} catch (e) {\n  return [{ json: { _not_a_receipt: true } }];\n}\n\nif (!parsed.items || !Array.isArray(parsed.items) || parsed.items.length === 0) {\n  return [{ json: { _not_a_receipt: true } }];\n}\n\nconst executionId = $execution.id;\nconst receiptMeta = {\n  receipt_id: executionId,\n  store_name: parsed.store_name ?? null,\n  store_branch: parsed.store_branch ?? null,\n  store_address: parsed.store_address ?? null,\n  store_postcode: parsed.store_postcode ?? null,\n  receipt_date: parsed.receipt_date ?? null,\n  receipt_time: parsed.receipt_time ?? null,\n  currency: parsed.currency ?? 'GBP',\n  subtotal: parsed.subtotal ?? null,\n  discount_total: parsed.discount_total ?? null,\n  tax_amount: parsed.tax_amount ?? null,\n  total_amount: parsed.total_amount ?? null,\n  payment_method: parsed.payment_method ?? null,\n  last4_card_digits: parsed.last4_card_digits ?? null,\n  loyalty_programme: parsed.loyalty_programme ?? null,\n  source_image_url: $('Webhook').item.json.body.attachments[0].url,\n  discord_user: $('Webhook').item.json.body.author.username,\n  created_at: new Date().toISOString(),\n};\n\nreturn parsed.items.map(item => ({\n  json: {\n    ...receiptMeta,\n    line_number: item.line_number,\n    product_name: item.product_name,\n    normalised_name: item.normalised_name,\n    category: item.category,\n    quantity: item.quantity,\n    unit: item.unit ?? null,\n    unit_price: item.unit_price ?? null,\n    line_total: item.line_total ?? null,\n    is_discount_line: item.is_discount_line ?? false,\n    discount_amount: item.discount_amount ?? null,\n    is_taxable: item.is_taxable ?? false,\n    tax_rate_percent: item.tax_rate_percent ?? 0,\n    brand: item.brand ?? null,\n    sku_or_barcode: item.sku_or_barcode ?? null,\n  }\n}));\n"
      },
